                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8906" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0974</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1142 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海尔链群合约：物联网时代下开放式创新模式升级迭代成功之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Haier Chain Group Contract：The Road to Successful Upgrade and Iteration of Open Innovation Models in the Internet of Things Era</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蒋石梅，覃欣然，徐思远，杨凯迪，郭雨芯，徐烁华</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海尔集团公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海尔集团；开放式创新；链群合约；知识共享；人单合一</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Haier Group; Open innovation; Knowledge sharing; Integrating order with personnel</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海尔集团是世界第四大白色家电制造商，也是中国电子信息百强企业之首。2024年以来，海尔已连续15年蝉联全球大型家用电器品牌零售量第一。并且海尔作为全球唯一的物联网生态品牌，已连续五年入选“Brand Z全球最具价值品牌百强”榜单，成为家电行业中的璀璨明星，续写着它的“海尔传奇”。纵观海尔的发展史，其开放式创新之路也独树一帜。从1985年海尔“砸冰箱”事件的出现到2020年“链群合约”的正式提出再到今天，海尔在家电行业四十年探索的同时，也在开放式创新路上走了整整四十年。海尔通过知识共享模式变革推动开放式创新模式升级迭代，以创新引领发展，最后形成独特的竞争优势。本文以海尔的开放式创新发展过程为主线，旨在通过对海尔开放式创新路径迭代升级的过程进行解析，引领学生掌握开放式创新的内涵、路径与驱动因素等知识点，深刻理解创新的本质。同时，启发学生思考企业在不同发展阶段如何通过知识共享模式变革推动开放式创新的涌现和升级迭代，加强企业的动态能力。在此基础上，讨论海尔开放式创新的成功经验在推广中所具有的价值与意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Haier Group is the world&#39;s fourth-largest white goods manufacturer and one of China&#39;s top 100 electronic information companies. It has been the world&#39;s No. 1 retailer of large household appliances for 15 consecutive years since 2024. As the world&#39;s only Internet of Things eco-brand, Haier has been listed in the &quot;Brand Z Top 100 Most Valuable Brands in the World&quot; for five consecutive years and has become a shining star in the home appliance industry, continuing its &quot;Haier Legend.&quot; Throughout the history of Haier&#39;s development, Haier&#39;s open innovation road has also been unique. From the emergence of Haier&#39;s &quot;smashing the refrigerator&quot; event in 1985 to the formal proposal of the &quot;chain group contract&quot; in 2020 to today, it has been exploring the home appliance industry for forty years, and at the same time, Haier has been on the road of open innovation for forty years. Haier has upgraded and iterated its open innovation model by prying the change of knowledge sharing mode, leading the development with innovation, and finally realizing its unique competitive advantage. This paper takes Haier&#39;s open innovation development process as the main line and aims to lead students to master the connotation, path, and driving factors of open innovation and deeply understand the essence of innovation by analyzing the iterative upgrading process of Haier&#39;s open innovation path. At the same time, students are inspired to think about how enterprises can promote the emergence and upgrading of open innovation through the change of the knowledge-sharing model at different stages of development so as to strengthen their dynamic capability. On this basis, the value and significance of Haier&#39;s successful experience with open innovation in promotion are discussed.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">开放式创新；知识共享</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
